for another approach.

00:19:53.482 --> 00:19:55.916
This approach, of course,
still can't replace

00:19:55.917 --> 00:19:59.987
the input from the people
with disabilities, but it can address

00:19:59.988 --> 00:20:03.357
some of the issues
with simulating disabilities,

00:20:03.358 --> 00:20:08.997
and that is simulating barriers,

00:20:09.631 --> 00:20:13.467
but wait, didn't
