00:20:24.212 --> 00:20:26.857
so what am I even talking about?

00:20:27.883 --> 00:20:30.985
Let me give you an example,
which we will use to explain

00:20:30.986 --> 00:20:35.984
the difference, and why I think
this might be a better approach.

00:20:36.124 --> 00:20:38.159
A simple and crude way to simulate

00:20:38.160 --> 00:20:41.095
visual impairment
