00:23:07.242 --> 00:23:09.877
Let's talk about
some of the limitations,

00:23:09.878 --> 00:23:14.083
and potential new issues
that come with this approach.

00:23:17.285 --> 00:23:21.989
While simulating barriers
is a step forward, it is not magic.

00:23:21.990 --> 00:23:23.524
The obvious first step first issue

00:23:23.525 --> 00:23:27.027
is that it can't be seen
as a plug and play

00:23:27.028 --> 00:23:30.678
replacement for
the simulation of disabilities.

00:23:30.932 --> 00:23:33.041
To explain what I mean by this,

00:23:33.042 --> 00:23:36.236
let's take the simulation
